Paper: hep-th/9903150

Date: 1999-03-17

Title: Z_2-Graded Cocycles in Higher Dimensions

Authors: C. Ekstrand

Comments: 19 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 43 (1998) 359-378

Current superalgebras and corresponding Schwinger terms in 1 and 3 spacedimensions are studied. This is done by generalizing the quantization of chiralfermions in an external Yang-Mills potential to the case of a Z_2-gradedpotential coupled to bosons and fermions.